						<summary>

						<p>This is unfinished, and seems to record some provision made in money for burning a perpetual lamp in the temple of Tirumēṟṟaḷi-Mahādēva at [Tiruveṅgai]vāyil in Peruvāyil-nāḍu by a native of <hi rend="bold">Kalaimaṅgalam in Kaviram</hi> (Kavira-nāḍu) a division of Valla-nāḍu.</p>						

						</summary>
